    <string name="help_text">Welcome to Phlogging!
                Phlogging is just like blogging, except for your phone. This app has several features to assist you in creating your phlog entries.
                \n\n
                Press Create, which will allow you to make your phlog entry! Once there, type in a title and some text. 
                To add media to your phlog entry, simply pull up or press the Media Drawer at the bottom of the screen.
                \n\n
                Tap on an entry in the list view at any time to display your phlog entry! From here you can view your thoughts and media contained within your phlog post!
                Simply tap Delete to remove the entry, or Edit to make changes to it.
                \n\n
                Enjoy and happy phlogging!</string>

